name: Potion
summary: Slightly heals one MegaBit.

name: Mega Potion
summary: Moderately heals one MegaBit.

name: Giga Potion
summary: Critically heals one MegaBit.

name: Energy Potion
summary: Restores a large portion of your MegaBits energy.

name: Capture Card
summary: Used to capture and store wild MegaBits.

name: Mega Card
summary: Used to capture and store wild MegaBits. Has a better chance of success than a standard Capture Card.

name: Giga Card
summary: Used to capture and store wild MegaBits. Has a much better chance of success than a standard Capture Card.

name: Mega Boost
summary: Significantly raises all of one MegaBit's stats in battle.

name: Giga Boost
summary: Drastically raises all of one MegaBit's stats in battle.

name: Sleep Cure
summary: Wakes one sleeping MegaBit.

name: Burn Cure
summary: Heals one burned MegaBit.

name: Poison Cure
summary: Heals one poisoned MegaBit.

name: Cure
summary: Cures any one status ailment.

name: Attack Boost
summary: Temporarily raises one MegaBit's Attack stat in battle.

name: Defense Boost
summary: Temporarily raises one MegaBit's Defense stat in battle.

name: Accuracy Boost
summary: Temporarily raises one MegaBit's Accuracy stat in battle.

name: Speed Boost
summary: Temporarily raises one MegaBit's Speed stat in battle.

name: Stat Boost
summary: Slightly raises all of one MegaBit's stats in battle.

name: Amplify Move Chip
summary: @Raises the user's attack.

name: Cyclone Move Chip
summary: Traps the foe in a vortex of swirling air, dealing damage and preventing it from fleeing or switching.

name: Dive Bomb Move Chip
summary: The user plunges from high in the air to strike the foe with great speed.

name: Dog Fight Move Chip
summary: Deals ongoing damage and prevents both user and foe from switching out.

name: Implode Move Chip
summary: A huge burst of air deals massive damage to both MegaBits.

name: Pulmonate Move Chip
summary: Compresses the air around the foe: this deals damage and lowers the foe's defense.

name: Soar Move Chip
summary: The user soars high into the air, preparing for its next attack.

name: Sonic Boom Move Chip
summary: An extremely powerful shockwave disorients the foe, decreasing its accuracy.

name: Arc Tackle Move Chip
summary: An electrically charged tackle.

name: Delete Move Chip
summary: Knocks out the foe instantly.

name: Discharge Move Chip
summary: @Boosts crit rate at the cost of health

name: Electrocute Move Chip
summary: @Recoil, chance of paralysis,

name: Spark Move Chip
summary: Zaps the foe with an electrical shock.

name: Static Burst Move Chip
summary: Disorients the foe with a burst of static, decreasing its speed and accuracy.

name: Thunder Smash Move Chip
summary: An electrically overcharged tackle that also hurts the user.

name: Blaze Move Chip
summary: The user blazes with spiritual fire, taking some health damage in order to boost energy.

name: Cinder Smash Move Chip
summary: Bombards the foe with volcanic rock, potentially burning it.

name: Flametongue Move Chip
summary: @Burns the foe.

name: Immolate Move Chip
summary: Hits the foe with fire almost as hot as the surface of the sun.

name: Oxidize Move Chip
summary: A small, focused burst of heat decreases the foe's defense.

name: Rain of Fire Move Chip
summary: Deals immediate and continued damage to to the foe at the cost of one-time recoil damage to the user.

name: Scorch Move Chip
summary: @Singes the foe.

name: Smolder Move Chip
summary: Scorching flames inflict a burn on the foe.

name: Bio Beam Move Chip
summary: A beam of powerful live energy hammers the foe, causing massive damage.

name: Bloom Move Chip
summary: Slightly heals the user and raises its attack.

name: Ensnare Move Chip
summary: Entangles the foe with spiky vines that deal damage and prevent it from using any moves.

name: Evergreen Move Chip
summary: Heals a small amount of damage every turn.

name: Prune Move Chip
summary: Sacrifices a small amount of health to raise all of the user's other stats.

name: Root Move Chip
summary: Sends down a deep taproot, healing the user and increasing its defense.

name: Sap Move Chip
summary: Saps the foe's health.

name: Venom Move Chip
summary: Injects the foe with a deadly toxin.

name: Avalanche Move Chip
summary: Hits the foe with a massive wall of ice and cold air.

name: Freeze Move Chip
summary: Ice crystals crystallize from the air, slowing the foe and dealing it damage when it moves.

name: Frostbite Move Chip
summary: Reduces the temperature around the foe to subzero temperatures, lowering the foe's speed.

name: Hail Move Chip
summary: Deals damage over time, and temporarily decreases the foe's speed.

name: Ice Spike Move Chip
summary: The foe is pinned down by an icy spike, dealing damage and causing them to flinch.

name: Snowstorm Move Chip
summary: Pelts the foe with snow and ice. May cause freezing.

name: Sublimate Move Chip
summary: Surrounds the foe with steam, reducing its accuracy.

name: Fracture Move Chip
summary: Splits open the foe's defenses to deal a great amount of damage.

name: Iron Defense Move Chip
summary: Negates the foe's next move by increasing the user's defense.

name: Quake Move Chip
summary: Quake deals massive damage to the foe and reduces their accuracy. It has a low hit rate, making it an unpredictable move.

name: Quicksand Move Chip
summary: Traps the foe in a pit of quicksand, reducing it's speed and preventing it from fleeing or switching.

name: Refine Move Chip
summary: The user shrugs off any status effects.

name: Rock Wall Move Chip
summary: @Dramatically increase users defense

name: Splinter Move Chip
summary: Shards of rock damage the foe over time.

name: Alternate Move Chip
summary: Forces the foe to switch out or run away.

name: Drain Move Chip
summary: @Drains energy/Health

name: Evil Eye Move Chip
summary: @The foe becomes uneasy and loses energy

name: Funeral Pyre Move Chip
summary: An eruption of spiritual fire knocks out both the user and the foe.

name: Hex Move Chip
summary: @Removes energy every turn

name: Hypnotize Move Chip
summary: @An enchanting song that puts the foe to sleep.

name: Omen Move Chip
summary: @Increase crit rate

name: Soulfire Move Chip
summary: @Regain energy over time

name: Bite Move Chip
summary: A swift attack with sharp teeth.

name: Focus Move Chip
summary: The user enters an extremely focused state, increasing its chances to deal a critical hit.

name: Fury Move Chip
summary: @enrage increasing crit/attack

name: Headbutt Move Chip
summary: An old reliable favorite: a solid headbutt.

name: Shuffle Move Chip
summary: @Do the Ali shuffle

name: Stutter Punch Move Chip
summary: A martial arts technique that delivers at least one punch.

name: Sucker Punch Move Chip
summary: A hit that can deal twice the normal amount of damage when the foe is at full health.

name: Swift Kick Move Chip
summary: A simple kick.

name: Cleanse Move Chip
summary: @Removes all status conditions from both foes

name: Dunk Move Chip
summary: Plunges the foe into deep water, preventing it from moving the next turn.

name: Flood Move Chip
summary: Submerges the foe in an unavoidable deluge of water.

name: Gel Move Chip
summary: Encapsulates the foe in a viscous fluid that dramatically slows it down.

name: Plunge Move Chip
summary: The user plunges deep into the water, preparing for its next attack.

name: Riptide Move Chip
summary: Sweeps the foe up in a huge wave, forcibly switching it out in a trainer battle (or causing it to run in the wild.)

name: Squirt Gun Move Chip
summary: Hits the foe with a high-pressure jet of water.

name: Torrent Move Chip
summary: Strikes the foe with repeated blasts of water.

name: Undertow Move Chip
summary: A massive current sweeps the foe away, knocking it out instantly.
